What s New We have introduced the Subtitle Mode so that users with hearing impaired could enjoy a conversation Podcasts or even movies by reading the audio converted text. Starting from version 3.4.0 we also implemented a Dynamic Language Model so that supported languages could be robustly updated. Better yet we now happily and proudly! announced that the ENGLISH version of the service is now available! Bug Fixes Fixed srt file time code format There was an error message informing you network error when you delete a transcript. We have removed this false alarm so that you won t see it pop up every time you try to delete a transcript.
